snippet.title: Best VGM 1378 - Little Nemo : The Dream Master - Nightmare World
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Little Nemo : The Dream Master (1990)
Nightmare World
Junko Tamiya
